node.text:
Hiii Friends 👋🏼 Was super encouraged this morning by this and thought I’d pop on and share for someone out there !!! The the Lord has huge plans for you & is not done w you yet!!

“For God’s gifts and His call are irrevocable” -Romans 11:29 ⛅️

Do you know what that means?? That means that no matter how bad you think you’ve messed up, no matter how unqualified you think you are or even those around you say you are, God has already chosen and called you and will NEVER take that calling away!! He doesn’t give up on us when things get tough. And He is a promise keeper! 

Philippians 1:6 says “being confident of this, that he who began a good work in you will carry it on to completion until the day of Christ Jesus.” 

He will be faithful to complete what He’s started in our lives if we will just continue to trust Him at His word and cling to Him in the good and bad times!! 

So take this as your reminder today to keep enduring and let your heart be encouraged because we are so loved by our creator, we have a purpose, and we already have victory through Him!!! Love y’all 🤍
